   =20
 =20
Goldman Sachs Traders Deliver Surprise Surge in Firm=E2=80=99s  Best Year E=
ver. Wall Street Bosses See Windfall Lasting, Fueling  Pay and Hiring. Chin=
a Breaks Silence on  Evergrande, Says Risks Controllable. Will  WeWork Work=
? Oil Hits  $85 a Barrel With Global Energy Costs Soaring. Italy Nears Deal=
